Jimmy, this is utter and total entrapment.

36:04.453 --> 36:06.455
Do not speak again until I tell you to.

36:06.581 --> 36:10.126
-I want to speak to my client in private.
-I had no intention of harming her,

36:10.209 --> 36:12.920
and these people had a bogus flat
on the way in.

36:13.087 --> 36:15.464
Shut up or get another lawyer.
I want his cuffs off.

36:15.715 --> 36:18.176
-I wanna speak to him in private.
-You want that done here?

36:18.634 --> 36:19.886
Right here would be fine.

36:20.636 --> 36:21.762
ARTHUR: Take off his cuffs.

36:22.305 --> 36:25.057
-They won't wanna be using the pokey room.
-ARTHUR: Interview three.

36:25.349 --> 36:27.018
-I believe that's down the hall.
-ARTHUR: Yeah.

36:27.977 --> 36:31.022
-SINCLAIR: Hmm. You do look lovely.
-Thanks a lot.

36:32.315 --> 36:35.651
Yeah, if she was drawn to plague carriers,
the feeling might be mutual.

36:35.860 --> 36:37.111
It's amazing how many are.

36:37.445 --> 36:40.239
(INHALES) Leo, I'm gonna be a few moments
with Mr. Cullinan.

36:40.323 --> 36:42.283
Then you and I can have a moment
in the coffee room.

36:43.826 --> 36:44.827
Boys.

36:51.876 --> 36:53.377
You want me to wear this home?

36:54.086 --> 36:55.588
I don't care what you do.

36:57.465 --> 36:58.466
(EXHALES)

37:01.928 --> 37:04.805
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

37:04.972 --> 37:09.185
